data.description: Welcome home to this well-maintained 3 bed 1.75 bath rambler built by Ashby Homes in a charming community. Cozy up in this beautiful, open-concept living space with a year-round outdoor patio. This quality home boasts a large kitchen made for entertaining to include a butlers pantry with wine fridge and gorgeous granite countertops. The large primary bedroom has a walk in closet and ¾ bath with walk-in shower. Beautiful landscaping and fully fenced back yard for privacy. Enjoy quick access to downtown Shelton, healthcare facilities, restaurants, shopping and more.
